<div class="blog-booklist-text"><a href="https://www.thirdplacebooks.com/book/9781647421731" target="_blank"><em><strong>Heart Radical: A Search for Language, Love, and Belonging</strong></em></a> by&nbsp;Anne Liu Kellor<br />
<strong>Release Date: </strong>9/7/21<br />
<strong>Genre: </strong>Biography<br />
<strong>Price: </strong>$16.95

<p>Wanting to understand how her path is tied to her mother tongue, Anne, a young, multiracial American woman, travels through China, the country of her mother's birth. Along the way, she tries on different roles--seeker, teacher, student, girlfriend, artist, and daughter--and continually asks herself: Why do I feel called to make this journey?</p>
